beer.beer_description:
A complex stout steeped in our winemaking heritage. 

This special Extra Stout is a dark, moderately roasty and strong brew with notes of chocolate, caramel and dried fruits. That brew is then taken and aged in Hope Estate oak wine barrels, adding moreish flavours of vanilla, mocha and spice.
